{"thag2.1:0.1":"Theragatha 2.1 ","thag2.1:0.2":"Dukanipata ","thag2.1:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag2.1:0.4":"Uttarattheragatha ","thag2.1:1.1":"“Natthi koci bhavo nicco, ","thag2.1:1.2":"sankhara vapi sassata; ","thag2.1:1.3":"Uppajjanti ca te khandha, ","thag2.1:1.4":"cavanti aparaparam. ","thag2.1:2.1":"Etamadinavam natva, ","thag2.1:2.2":"bhavenamhi anatthiko; ","thag2.1:2.3":"Nissato sabbakamehi, ","thag2.1:2.4":"patto me asavakkhayo”ti. ","thag2.1:2.5":"Ittham sudam ayasma uttaro thero gathayo abhasitthati. "}